snippet: Avery Bradley matched his season-high with 27 points, and the Boston Celtics earned their fourth straight victory with a 111-103 win over the Denver Nuggets on Wednesday night....
lead_paragraph: Avery Bradley matched his season-high with 27 points, and the Boston Celtics earned their fourth straight victory with a 111-103 win over the Denver Nuggets on Wednesday night.

headline.main: Bradley Matches Season-High 27, Celtics Down Nuggets 111-103
headline.print_headline: Bradley Matches Season-High 27, Celtics Down Nuggets 111-103
